  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/850f6c7ba3ae09b4831876a4d6aad902.apng?t=1765606919\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/850f6c7ba3ae09b4831876a4d6aad902.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=120 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Okashi Towers is a Real Time Strategy game with Tower Defense elements. Gather candy resources to build defensive tower units or go on the offensive and summon creatures to attack other player bases. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/656c9ffbd4b19ad4b3867e1645ecd4da.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/656c9ffbd4b19ad4b3867e1645ecd4da.webm?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/656c9ffbd4b19ad4b3867e1645ecd4da.mp4?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mixture of tower defense and RTS. Control a base and spend candy resources to summon upgradable tower units to build defenses and increase the amount of candy resources received over time. Spend resources to summon offensive units that can be controlled individually in an RTS style to find and destroy enemy units and their base through fog of war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/2ee3cd3ba9fb7dd3b4da88062a597480.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/2ee3cd3ba9fb7dd3b4da88062a597480.webm?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/2ee3cd3ba9fb7dd3b4da88062a597480.mp4?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solo Story Mode Campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Online Multiplayer Up to 8 Players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play with any combination of up to 8 Teams and 8 Players (or NPCs)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create custom designed maps in the Map Builder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 Factions to choose from, each with a different play style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multi-language Support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/a4822b5143e6e731a83e7d33f5bcf858.apng?t=1765606919\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/a4822b5143e6e731a83e7d33f5bcf858.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=50 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Artwork by Shiruht</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/850f6c7ba3ae09b4831876a4d6aad902.apng?t=1765606919\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/850f6c7ba3ae09b4831876a4d6aad902.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=120 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Okashi Towers is a Real Time Strategy game with Tower Defense elements. Gather candy resources to build defensive tower units or go on the offensive and summon creatures to attack other player bases. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/656c9ffbd4b19ad4b3867e1645ecd4da.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/656c9ffbd4b19ad4b3867e1645ecd4da.webm?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/656c9ffbd4b19ad4b3867e1645ecd4da.mp4?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mixture of tower defense and RTS. Control a base and spend candy resources to summon upgradable tower units to build defenses and increase the amount of candy resources received over time. Spend resources to summon offensive units that can be controlled individually in an RTS style to find and destroy enemy units and their base through fog of war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/2ee3cd3ba9fb7dd3b4da88062a597480.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/2ee3cd3ba9fb7dd3b4da88062a597480.webm?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/2ee3cd3ba9fb7dd3b4da88062a597480.mp4?t=1765606919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solo Story Mode Campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Online Multiplayer Up to 8 Players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play with any combination of up to 8 Teams and 8 Players (or NPCs)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create custom designed maps in the Map Builder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 Factions to choose from, each with a different play style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multi-language Support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/a4822b5143e6e731a83e7d33f5bcf858.apng?t=1765606919\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450360/extras/a4822b5143e6e731a83e7d33f5bcf858.poster.avif?t=1765606919\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=50 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Artwork by Shiruht</p>",
